re ;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\">initially in 7 stages according to Rolf Faste3: define, search, imagine, prototyping, selecting, implementing, learning;</span></span></li>\r\n 	<li><span id=\"result_box\" class=\"\" lang=\"nl\"><span title=\"ramené à 5 par Jeremy Gutsche : définir, imaginer, synthétiser, prototyper, tester ;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\">reduced to 5 by Jeremy Gutsche: define, imagine, synthesize, prototyping, testing;</span></span></li>\r\n 	<li><span id=\"result_box\" class=\"\" lang=\"nl\"><span title=\"voire à 3 selon Tim Brown (IDEO)4 : inspiration, imagination, implémentation.\">or 3 according to Tim Brown (IDEO) 4: inspiration, imagination, implementation.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Design Thinking', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '192-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-02-06 11:12:19', '2018-02-06 10:12:19', '', 192, 'http://localhost/wordpress2/2018/02/06/192-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
